Legendary broadcaster Bob Mabena died on Monday after going into cardiac arrest. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Music industry greats are paying tribute to legendary broadcaster Bob Mabena in a memorial service in Johannesburg on Thursday afternoon. Mabena died on Monday after going into cardiac arrest. READ: Bob Mabena remembered His radio career has lasted over 30-years, working at several radio stations. At the time of his passing, he was a presenter of Power Breakfast on Power FM and station manager. Mabena will be laid to rest on Saturday.